[{'action': 'opened', 'author': 'ericnakagawa', 'comment_id': None, 'datetime': '2017-11-30T23:34:05Z', 'masked_author': 'username_0', 'text': 'Perhaps a bulk method for managing these -- especially helpful for an existing site migrating to Docusaurus.

